ax<br />\n<br />\n呢堆諗清楚先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黎搞笑嘅-Pulchra<br />\n更搞笑嘅-FOTS JAPAN  新名叫B&rsquo;full<br />\n運貨途中，產品會自動量子化<br />\n創造出極速腳軟傳說<br />\n組裝好個半鐘已經腳軟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G0uD7Pe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG0uD7Pe.gif&h=a56f6fef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPlum<br />\nInsight <br />\n呢幾間都係同一個集團黎，出名用料，QC垃圾"},{"pid":"05550e423881d5ca1ff81c71ee4ad1cf064518ce","tid":2117677,"uid":49044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T04:25:04.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"544debc8415b5a1dc7ee9ea0fed3042149cf946c","tid":2117677,"uid":49044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T04:25:35.000Z","msg":"點解係動物台唔係玩具台"},{"pid":"f7c2e4482cfe7190ccd9b73bfab8b88ad40adbaf","tid":2117677,"uid":188772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"544debc8415b5a1dc7ee9ea0fed3042149cf946c","tid":2117677,"uid":49044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T04:25:35.000Z","msg":"點解係動物台唔係玩具台"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T04:39:04.000Z","msg":"因為開錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}